搼字的汉语字典释义

[①]［quán］
［《廣韻》巨員切，平仙，羣。］
亦作“搼1”。
(1)手；卷手。
(2)拳头。
(3)指鸟兽的趾爪。
(4)搏击；拳击。
(5)力气；勇力。
(6)拳术。一种徒手的武术。
(7)真挚。
(8)卷曲；弯曲。
(9)见“拳母”。
(10)量词。用于以拳击人的动作。
(11)量词。块。
(12)量词。桩；注。
(13)通“弮”。弩弓。

[①]［quán］
["Guangyun" giant cut, flat fairy, group. ]
Also known as "搼1".
(1) Hands; roll hands.
(2) Fist.
(3) Refers to the toes of birds and beasts.
(4) Fight; boxing.
(5) Strength; courage.
(6) Boxing. An unarmed martial art.
(7) Sincere.
(8) Curl; bend.
(9) See "Fist Mother".
(10) Quantifiers. Used to punch people's movements.
(11) Quantifiers. Piece.
(12) Quantifiers. Pile; note.
(13) Through "弮". crossbow.
